# TTS model assets — served from public/tts-assets/shared/ in dev (via
# symlink to the Voice repo's local copies). In prod they live at
# /shared/ on Oracle. Never commit the .onnx files to Reader — they're
# the output of Phase 1's Voice Studio scripts and belong to that repo.
/public/tts-assets

# ORT-Web's WASM backend + threaded worker are copied into public/ort/
# by `npm run copy-ort-wasm` (runs via pre-dev / pre-build). Source
# lives in node_modules/onnxruntime-web/dist/; we mirror it same-origin
# so cross-origin isolation (COOP/COEP) can load them without CORP
# edge cases.
/public/ort
